message.content:
1. The treatments contained soybean meal.
2. The treatments contained sunflower cake.
3. The soybean meal was substituted by sunflower cake in the treatments.
4. There were four substitution levels in the treatments.
5. The substitution levels were 0%, 33%, 66%, and 100% DM.
6. 0% DM substitution level means no soybean meal was replaced by sunflower cake.
7. 33% DM substitution level means one-third of the soybean meal was replaced by sunflower cake.
8. 66% DM substitution level means two-thirds of the soybean meal was replaced by sunflower cake.
9. 100% DM substitution level means all the soybean meal was replaced by sunflower cake.
